<p>Hmmm. We'll, if you dont like playing a mage, reroll it into something better! I personally have loved playing a mage. Cant really get into any other class. Anyways, ya, most of the classes in EQ need a overhaul with all the new expansions, mages, warriors, etc. But all in all its a pretty effective caster. Dont know where you get off flaming it...</p>
